# FormatOutput

**Associated Type**

The type this format style produces as output.

## Declaration

```swift
associatedtype FormatOutput
```

## Discussion

Conforming types in Foundation define this type as either [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/String] or [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/AttributedString].

## Declaring input and output types

- **FormatInput**: The type this format style accepts as input.
